title: Narrative

Compares the standard interactive <<.def "tabs">> macro with `<<.def "static-tabs">>` in `details` mode. Each tab becomes a `<details open>` block with its caption inside `<summary>`.

+
title: Output

;Interactive tabs (default)

<<tabs "[[SampleTabOne]] [[SampleTabTwo]] [[SampleTabThree]] [[SampleTabFour]]" "SampleTabOne" "$:/state/test/static-tabs/outer">>

-----

;Explicit static-tabs, details mode

<<static-tabs "[[SampleTabOne]] [[SampleTabTwo]] [[SampleTabThree]] [[SampleTabFour]]" "" "" "h2" "demo" "details">>
